</p><fig class="- topic/fig " id="GUID-24AE04DF-FD44-4A9D-BE15-560933FCCA6A"><title class="- topic/title ">Location of the ink system (marked yellow)</title><image class="- topic/image " href="GUID-29EF68F7-48D5-4AD5-A431-323D06E1D15F-low.png" placement="inline" otherprops="GUID-29EF68F7-48D5-4AD5-A431-323D06E1D15F-low.png"/></fig></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Functional description</category></metadata></prolog><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><section id="GUID-F5034822-753A-4C8B-A7CD-E44CE7EBD702" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title "><ph class="- topic/ph ">Definition</ph></title><p class="- topic/p ">The function of the ink system is split up in different functional sections as described below. 
