</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Description 
</p></entry></row></thead><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Ink tank (1) 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">There are 4 or 5 ink tanks (one for each color Y,C,M,K and W) in the system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">For detailed information see : 
<xref keyref="02FUNC03" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-CEB0B358-F9CC-4CB3-928B-03878F8B8A01.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="concept"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>02 The function of the ink tank</xref> / 
