</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Ink bottle (2) 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Ink bottles of 0.7 liter are used to refill the ink tanks. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">For detailed information see : 
<xref keyref="02FUNC04" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-65801C08-0C00-4779-92DB-79F805618990.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="concept"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>02 The function of the ink bottle</xref> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Ink tubes (3) and pumps (4) 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Pumps are used to pump the ink from the tanks through the tubes to the printheads. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">For detailed information see : 
<xref keyref="02FUNC05" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-0743CE4B-4B8E-4315-889B-B4B37348F19F.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="concept"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text xref?>02 The function of the ink tubes and pumps</xref> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The <comp class="+ topic/ph oce-d/comp "><compname class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compname ">Ink supply PBA</compname><compcodenr translate="no" class="+ topic/keyword oce-d/compcodenr "> 02PBA01 </compcodenr></comp> 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">The ink supply PBA controls the ink system. 
</p><p class="- topic/p ">For detailed information see : 
